The paper discusses a data structure for collaborative text editing and versioning, which falls under the category of distributed systems and data structures. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Other relevant sub-categories include cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.SC (Symbolic Computation and Formal Languages), cs.SD (Software Development), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
